{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "35792e21-213c-4766-bef0-fb13f7643d12", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/35792e21-213c-4766-bef0-fb13f7643d12@3.pkg/1772597568244/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597568481", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/35792e21-213c-4766-bef0-fb13f7643d12@3.pkg/1772597568244/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597568481"}, "identifier": "35792e21-213c-4766-bef0-fb13f7643d12", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>一审题干；二审设问；三审题肢。</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>D：依据教材知识，宪法通过设置国家机构，授予国家机构特定职权，明确国家机构的组成、任期、工作方式等内容，使国家权力的运行稳定有序。从宪法第一百三十四条及一百三十六条规定的内容说明了宪法设置国家机构，并授予其职权，故D符合题意；</p>\n\n<p>AB：题文体现的是宪法设置国家机构，并授予其相应的职权。材料没有体现宪法是党的主张和人民意志的统一、人民检察院及其工作人员越权了。故AB不符合题意；</p>\n\n<p>C：人民检察院独立行使检察权，不受行政机关、社会团体和个人的干涉，但要受到人民代表大会的监督，故C说法错误。</p>\n\n<p>故本题选D。</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p>（改编·2024山东日照中考真题）中华人民共和国宪法</p>\n\n<table border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width:568px\">\n\t\t\t<p>第一百三十四条：中华人民共和国人民检察院是国家的法律监督机关。</p>\n\n\t\t\t<p>第一百三十六条：人民检察院依照法律规定独立行使检察权，不受行政机关、社会团体和个人的干涉。</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>由上述条文可知（&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n", "title": "（改编·2024山东日照中考真题）中华人民共和国宪法第一百三十四条：中华人民共和国人民检察院是国家的法律监督机关。第一百三十六条：人民检察院依照法律规定独立行使检察权，不受行政机关、社会团体和个人的干涉。由上述条文可知（    ）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["D"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/35792e21-213c-4766-bef0-fb13f7643d12@3.pkg/item.json?v=1754822305488", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "choice_type": "character", "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>人民检察院及其工作人员不可越权</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>宪法是党的主张和人民意志的统一</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>检察机关公正司法，不受任何监督</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<p>宪法设置国家机构，并授予其职权</p>\n"}], "prompt": "<p>（改编·2024山东日照中考真题）中华人民共和国宪法</p>\n\n<table border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width:568px\">\n\t\t\t<p>第一百三十四条：中华人民共和国人民检察院是国家的法律监督机关。</p>\n\n\t\t\t<p>第一百三十六条：人民检察院依照法律规定独立行使检察权，不受行政机关、社会团体和个人的干涉。</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>由上述条文可知（&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source": {"container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "tags": ["$M002000000", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "ff8080814371757b014390fcdce504bd", "5136342960", "44bec67a-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "$RE0000", "$M003002000", "5036342749", "$RE0200", "6a74973a-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "$RE0201", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5", "44bee8bc-54e6-1